[{"Id": 1010054, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "In the book of Tuhfat al-Zaaer, Imam Sadiq (a), is reported to have said that one who wants his request to be granted by Almighty Allah or fears something, may write down the following supplication on a white patch and then fold it and put it in a dried round clay and throw it in current water. Verily, Almighty Allah will relieve one who does so from grievances…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Tuhfat al Zaaer mein Imam Sadiq (a) se marwi hai keh kisi momin ko jab koi haajat, darr ya kisi maamle mein khouf la-haq ho to woh ek safeed kaaghaz (white paper) par yeh dua likkhe aur uske neeche apni haajat ka zikr kare. Phir us kaaghaz ko mitti mein lapet kar aabe jaari (running water) ya kunwe (well) mein daal de, Inshallah Khuda wande kareem jald hi yeh haajat puri farmaayega…", "UrduDescription": "تحفۃ الزائر میں امام جعفر صادق ؑ سے مروی ہے :کسی مومن کو جب کوئی حاجت درپیش ہو یا کسی معاملے میں خوف لاحق ہو تو وہ ایک کاغذ پر یہ عبارت لکھے۔ لفظ کذا و کذا کے بجائے اپنی حاجت کا تذکرہ کرے پھر اس کاغذ کو مٹی میں لپیٹ کر آبِ جاری یا کنویں میں ڈال دے۔ انشاء اللہ خداوند کریم جلد ہی یہ حاجت پوری فرمادے گا۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "Ar