": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010055, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Mai Teri taraf aaya hu ba-waasta Tere sab se pasandida naam ke jo Tere nazdeek sab naamo se azeem hai. Tera qurb chahta aur Tere huzoor wasila banaaya hai usko jis ka haq Tu ne khud par laazim thairaaya wasila banaaya hai. Muhammad (s.a.w.a), Ali (a.s), Fatema (s.a), Hasan (a.s), Husain (a.s) ko aur wasila banaaya hai Ali bin Husain (a.s), Muhammad bin Ali (a.s), Jafar bin Muhammad (a.s), Moosa bin Jafar (a.s), Ali bin Moosa (a.s), Muhammad bin Ali (a.s), Ali bin Muhammad (a.s), Hasan bin Ali (a.s) aur wasila banaaya hai Hujjat Muntazar (a.t.f.s) ko. Khuda ka durood ho un sab Masoomeen (a.s) par. Khudaaya mera yeh aur yeh kaam bana de…", "Urdu": "خدا کے نام سے شروع جو بڑا رحم والا مہربان ہے اے معبود! میں تیری طرف آیا ہوں تیرے سب سے پسندیدہ نام کے واسطے سےجو تیرے نزدیک سب ناموں سے عظیم ہے تیرا تقرب چاہا اور تیرے حضور وسیلہ بنایا ہے اس کو جس کا حق تو نے خود پر لازم ٹھہرایا وسیلہ بنایاہے محمدؐ، علی ؑ، فاطمہ ؑ، حسن ؑ، حسین ؑ، کو اور وسیلہ بنایا ہے علی ؑابن الحسینؑ، محمدؑ ابن علیؑ، جعفرؑ ابن محمدؑ کو اور موؑسیٰ ابن جعفرؑ، علیؑ ابن موسیٰؑ،محمدؑا بن علیؑ، علیؑ ابن محمدؑ اور حسنؑ ابن علی ؑ کو اور وسیلہ بنایا ہے حجتِ منتظر ؑ کو خدا کا درود ہو ان سب معصومین ؑ پر خدایا! میرا یہ اور یہ کام بنا دے۔۔۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNEE ATA-WAJJAHU ILAIY-KA BE-AHAB-BIL ASMAA-E ILAIY-KA WA A’ZAME-HAA LADAIY-KA WA ATA-QARRA-BO WA ATA-WASSA-LO ILAIY-KA BE-MAN AW-JABTA HAQQA-HU E’LAIY-KA BE-MOHAMMADIW WA A’LIYYIN WA FAATE-MATA WAL HASANE WAL HUSAIYNE WA A’LIYYIB NIL HUSAIYNE WA MOHAMMA-DIB-NE A’LIYYIN WA JA’FA-RIB-NE MOHAMMADIN WA MOO-SAB-NE JA’FARIN WA A’LIYYIB-NE MOOSAA WA MOHAMMA-DIB-NE A’LIYYIN WA A’LAIYYIB-NE MOHAMMADIN WAL HASA-NIB-NE A’LIYYIN WAL HUJJA-TIL MUNTA-ZARE SALAWAA-TUL LAAHE A’LAIY-HIM AJMA-EE’-NAK FENEE…", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّيْ اَتَوَجَّهٗ اِلَيْكَ بِاَحَبِّ الْاَسْمَاۗءِ اِلَيْكَ وَاَعْظَمِهَا لَدَيْكَ وَاَتَقَرَّبُ وَاَتَوَسَّلُ اِلَيْكَ بِمَنْ اَوْجَبْتَ حَقَّهٗ عَلَيْكَ بِمُحَمَّدٍ وَّعَلِيٍّ وَفَاطِمَةَ وَالْحَسَنِ وَالْحُسَيْنِ وَعَلِيِّ بْنِ الْحُسَيْنِ وَمُحَمَّدِ بْنِ عَلِيٍّ وَجَعْفَرِ بْنِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَمُوْسَى بْنِ جَعْفَرٍ وَعَلِيِّ بْنِ مُوْسٰى وَمُحَمَّدِ بْنِ عَلِيٍّ وَعَلِيِّ بْنِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَالْحَسَنِ بْنِ عَلِيٍّ وَ لْحُجَّةِ الْمُنْتَظَرِ صَلَوَاتُ اللهِ عَلَيْهِمْ اَجْمَعِيْنَ اكْفِنِيْ۔۔۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": nu